description:
The 2023 Honda Civic Sport is an exceptional vehicle that has recently seen a price drop of $811, making it an even more attractive option for those seeking a blend of performance, safety, and technology. This limited-time opportunity should not be missed, so act quickly to secure your Civic Sport before prices potentially rise again!

Under the hood, the Civic Sport houses a powerful 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivering a robust 158 horsepower through a CVT continuously variable transmission. This combination not only ensures a smooth driving experience but also offers excellent fuel efficiency, making it ideal for both city commuting and long road trips.

Among the standout features of the Civic Sport is its *Smart device mirroring* capability. This innovative technology allows you to seamlessly connect your smartphone to the vehicles infotainment system, enhancing convenience and keeping your focus on the road. With this feature, accessing your favorite apps is effortless, revolutionizing your driving experience without the need for manufacturer-specific applications.

Safety remains a top priority in the Civic Sport, highlighted by its *Forward collision mitigation* system. This proactive feature detects potential collisions and activates measures to help prevent or minimize impact severity. Additionally, the *Front pedestrian impact prevention* system constantly monitors the road for pedestrians, ensuring the safety of both drivers and pedestrians.

Another impressive addition is the *Hands-on steering assist/lane centering* feature, making long drives feel effortless. This advanced cruise control system maintains a safe distance from surrounding vehicles while keeping you centered in your lane. Just set your desired speed and let the technology take care of the rest.

The *Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go* feature further enhances convenience by automatically adjusting your speed to match the vehicle ahead, making stop-and-go traffic a breeze. Coupled with the *Lane departure prevention* system, the Civic Sport significantly enhances your overall driving experience by keeping you safely within designated lanes.

For added safety, the *Rear camera* assists in navigating tight spaces, while the *Brake assist* feature ensures quick reactions to unexpected situations. Plus, the *Keyfob vehicle start control* allows you to remotely start your engine, ensuring your vehicle is ready and comfortable before you step inside.

In summary, the 2023 Honda Civic Sport is an exceptional choice for modern drivers, excelling in performance, safety, and cutting-edge technology. Don t miss this opportunity to experience the future of driving act now!

While great effort is made to ensure the accuracy of the information on this site, errors do occur so please verify information with a customer service rep.

Central Ford is proud to offer this Blue Certified 2023 Honda Civic Hatchback Sport, finished in eye-catching Rallye Red with a sleek Black interior. With just 15,375 miles, this Civic is lightly driven and delivers the perfect balance of sporty design, efficiency, and everyday reliabilitynow backed by Fords Blue Certified coverage for added peace of mind.

Powered by a responsive 2.0L 4-cylinder i-VTEC engine paired with a smooth Sport CVT transmission, this front-wheel-drive hatchback offers confident performance and excellent fuel economy, rated at 29 MPG city / 37 MPG highway. Its versatile hatchback design adds practicality without sacrificing style.

The Sport trim enhances the Civics aggressive look with 18 alloy wheels, sport seating, and modern technology throughout the cabinmaking it a smart and fun daily driver.

Key Features:

Ford Blue Certified: Includes a 90-day/4,000-mile Comprehensive Limited Warranty, 14-point inspection, and roadside assistance.

2.0L 4-Cylinder Engine: Proven Honda reliability with strong efficiency and smooth power delivery.

Sport CVT Transmission: Optimized for responsive driving and fuel economy.

Honda Sensing Safety Suite: Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Keeping Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Road Departure Mitigation.

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto: Seamless smartphone integration for navigation, music, and calls.

Sport Exterior Styling: 18 alloy wheels, aggressive front fascia, and hatchback versatility.

Backup Camera: Added confidence when parking and maneuvering.

This 2023 Honda Civic Hatchback Sport delivers standout looks, trusted reliability, and modern safety technologyall with low miles and Blue Certified protection. Available now at Central Ford in Los Angeles.

Under the hood, the Malibu RS boasts a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a CVT transmission, delivering a smooth and efficient driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway, this sedan strikes the perfect balance between power and fuel economy.

The interior of the Malibu RS is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. The premium audio system, featuring Chevrolet Infotainment 3, keeps you connected and entertained on the road. The 8-way power driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel allow you to find the perfect driving position, while the rear window defroster and automatic climate control ensure a comfortable cabin no matter the weather.

Safety is also a top priority in the Malibu RS, with features like the Rear Cross Traffic Alert, Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, and a comprehensive airbag system providing you with peace of mind behind the wheel.

This Malibu RS is a true standout in its class, blending style, performance, and technology into a package that is sure to impress. description: The 2023 Honda Civic LX has recently seen a price drop of $-812, making this the perfect time to act if youre in the market for a reliable and innovative sedan. This vehicle, equipped with a robust 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivers an impressive 158HP through a continuously variable transmission CVT, blending performance with fuel efficiency seamlessly. Among its standout features is **Smart device mirroring**, which allows you to connect your smartphone to the vehicles infotainment system. This advanced technology ensures you can access your favorite apps without taking your eyes off the road, enhancing both safety and convenience. Safety is a priority in the Honda Civic LX, starting with the **Hands-on steering assist/lane centering** feature. This technology acts as your co-pilot, maintaining a safe distance from other vehicles while keeping you centered in your lane ideal for long journeys. Furthermore, the **Forward collision mitigation** system constantly monitors the road ahead, activating protective measures to help prevent or lessen the impact of potential accidents. In urban environments, the **Front pedestrian impact prevention** system is invaluable. It actively tracks pedestrians in your path, taking steps to avoid collisions and reinforcing Honda s commitment to road safety for all users. Additionally, the **Rear camera** provides enhanced visibility of obstacles behind you, making reversing safer and more efficient. Another impressive feature is the **Lane departure prevention** system, which corrects your vehicle s path if it drifts out of its lane without signaling, ensuring you stay on course. For those who frequently navigate stop-and-go traffic, the **Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go** feature is a significant advantage, automatically adjusting your vehicles speed to maintain a safe distance from the car in front, even bringing you to a stop when necessary. Other remarkable features include **Brake assist** for enhanced stopping power in emergencies and **Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls**, which enhances comfort on long drives. The **Touchscreen** interface offers intuitive control over various features, making it easier to stay connected and informed on the go. Overall, the 2023 Honda Civic LX is more than just a vehicle; it represents a perfect blend of power, safety, and cutting-edge technology. Dont miss out on this opportunity visit your local dealer today to experience the Civic LX for yourself! For over 50 years, Norm Reeves has continued to be a leader in the automotive retail industry serving all of Southern California. As an automotive group we represent over 18 different locations and 9 brands from Honda, Toyota, Ford, Lincoln, Hyundai, Genesis, Volkswagen, Subaru, and Mazda. Come in today to check out our selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and experience exceptional service you can trust!

Introducing the Certified 2023 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid Limited, featuring the exclusive *Option Group 01*. Recently, the price has dropped by $307, making this an enticing opportunity for potential buyers. With such a competitive price point, its essential to act quickly before this remarkable vehicle is gone!

The Sonata Hybrid Limited is powered by a Smartstream 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivering an impressive 150 horsepower coupled with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission. This efficient powertrain strikes an ideal balance between fuel economy and responsive performance, making it perfect for daily commutes or long road trips.

Among the standout features of the Sonata Hybrid Limited is the **Smart device mirroring** technology. This innovative feature allows seamless integration of your smartphone with the vehicles infotainment system, ensuring you can access vital apps without diverting your attention from the road. It enhances both safety and convenience, making every drive more enjoyable.

Safety is paramount in the Sonata Hybrid Limited, equipped with an advanced **Front pedestrian impact prevention** system. This technology actively monitors the road ahead, detecting pedestrians and taking proactive steps to avert potential accidents. With this feature, you can drive with confidence, knowing that the Sonata hybrid is looking out for you and others on the road.

The **Hands-on steering assist/lane centering** feature adds another layer of comfort during long drives. It helps maintain the vehicle s position within the lane with minimal effort from the driver, allowing for a more relaxed journey.

For those navigating heavy traffic, the **Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go** feature is invaluable. It automatically adjusts the vehicles speed, ensuring a safe distance from the car ahead, effectively reducing stress during stop-and-go conditions.

Comfort is also a priority with features like **Ventilated front seats** that provide refreshing airflow on hot days, and **Heated driver and front passenger seats** that deliver comforting warmth in colder weather.

In summary, the Certified 2023 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid Limited, with its advanced safety features, cutting-edge technology, and exceptional comfort options, sets a new benchmark for modern vehicles. Dont miss your chance to own this extraordinary car embrace the future of driving with the Sonata Hybrid Limited today! With a recent price drop, now is the perfect time to make this vehicle yours!

This stunning 2024 Subaru Crosstrek Premium is the perfect blend of versatility, capability, and style. With its spacious interior, advanced safety features, and impressive fuel efficiency, this Crosstrek is ready to take you on any adventure. The 2.0L 4-cylinder engine paired with Lineartronic CVT and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system delivers a smooth and confident ride, whether you're navigating city streets or tackling rugged terrain.

Boasting a sleek and modern exterior in a vibrant red hue, this Crosstrek Premium stands out from the crowd. The premium features, including the Crosstrek Mirror Package, Aero Crossbar Set, Rear Bumper Cover, and All-Weather Floor Liners, elevate the driving experience and provide added convenience and protection.

Inside, the Crosstrek Premium offers a spacious and well-appointed cabin, with premium cloth upholstery, a 11.6-inch STARLINK multimedia system, and a host of advanced technology features. The split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space make this SUV a practical choice for your everyday needs and weekend adventures.

This Crosstrek Premium is a certified pre-owned vehicle, which means it has been thoroughly inspected and comes with the added peace of mind of a comprehensive warranty. With low mileage and a clean CARFAX report, this Crosstrek is a true gem that you won't want to miss.

Located at Bob Penkhus South in Motor City Colorado Springs Exit 140, and also serving Canon City, Pueblo, Pueblo West, La Junta, Monument, Castle Rock, Alamosa, southern Colorado, and the greater Denver area.

Experience the epitome of modern style and performance with this impeccable 2024 Toyota Camry LE. Boasting a sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this Camry is the perfect blend of sophistication and capability.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this Camry LE is designed to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of:
Cold Weather Package
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
Automatic temperature control
Front dual zone A/C
Heated Exterior Mirrors
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
Multi-Stage Heated Front Seats

The Camry's 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and AWD, delivers a smooth and responsive ride, while the impressive fuel efficiency of 25 city/34 highway MPG* ensures you can go the distance with confidence.

Safety is paramount in this Camry, with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, including ABS brakes, Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags, Knee airbag, Rear side impact airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. You can drive with peace of mind, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Elevate your commute or weekend adventures with the impressive technology and convenience features of this Camry LE. Enjoy the seamless integration of your smartphone with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, stay connected with the Safety Connect emergency communication system, and keep your eyes on the road with the Rear Parking Camera and Auto High-beam Headlights.

This 2024 Toyota Camry LE is a true testament to the brand's commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. With a list price of $24,299, this exceptional vehicle represents exceptional value in the midsize sedan segment.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in the 2024 Kia Forte GT. This dynamic sedan is engineered to elevate your driving experience, offering a thrilling combination of power, efficiency, and advanced features.

At the heart of the Forte GT lies a 1.6L I4 Turbo engine, delivering an exhilarating 201 horsepower and 195 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth-shifting 7-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive, this powertrain ensures a responsive and engaging ride, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway.

- Automatic temperature control
- Front dual zone A/C
- Remote keyless entry
- Exterior Parking Camera Rear

- Illuminated entry

The Forte GT's sleek and dynamic exterior is complemented by a host of premium features, including 18" Alloy Wheels, Heated Door Mirrors, and a Rear Spoiler, giving it a striking and sporty presence on the road. Inside, the cabin is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, offering Cloth & SynTex Seat Trim, a Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel, and a Leather Shift Knob.

Experience the thrill of the open road with the 2024 Kia Forte GT's impressive fuel efficiency, boasting an EPA-estimated 27 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. With its advanced safety technologies, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, you can drive with confidence, knowing your protection is a top priority.

This exceptional Forte GT is currently available in Gray and priced at just $20,450. Don't miss your opportunity to own this dynamic and well-equipped sedan. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value and driving experience that the 2024 Kia Forte GT has to offer.

Central Ford is proud to showcase this Ford Blue Certified 2025 Nissan Rogue SV FWD, finished in sleek Gun Metallic with a modern Charcoal interior. With just 14,004 miles, this low-mile Rogue delivers near-new condition with the added confidence of Ford Blue Certified coverage.

Powered by a fuel-efficient 1.5L DOHC 12-valve turbocharged engine paired with an Xtronic CVT, the Rogue offers smooth performance and excellent efficiencyrated up to 37 MPG highway. Front-wheel drive provides confident daily driving with impressive ride comfort.

The SV trim adds smart technology and everyday convenience, making this Rogue an ideal compact SUV for commuting, road trips, or family duty. Advanced safety features and modern connectivity ensure peace of mind on every drive.

Key Features:

Ford Blue Certified: Includes a 90-day/4,000-mile Comprehensive Limited Warranty and 14-Month/7,000-Mile Powertrain Limited Warranty, plus a 139-point inspection and roadside assistance.

1.5L Turbocharged Engine: Delivers responsive performance with outstanding fuel economy.

SV Equipment Package: Features Intelligent Cruise Control, ProPILOT Assist, Remote Engine Start, and Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control.

Advanced Safety Shield 360: Includes Blind Spot Warning, Lane Departure Warning, Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert.

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto: Seamless smartphone integration through the NissanConnect infotainment system.

Rear View Monitor: Enhances visibility and confidence when parking or reversing.

This 2025 Nissan Rogue SV FWD combines efficiency, safety, and modern technology in a stylish, low-mile packagenow available with Blue Certified peace of mind at Central Ford in Los Angeles.

description:
Introducing the Certified 2025 Honda Civic Sport! Recently, the price has dropped by $500, making it an excellent time to act quickly and secure this outstanding vehicle. With its blend of style, efficiency, and cutting-edge technology, the Honda Civic Sport promises an exhilarating driving experience you wont want to miss.

Under the hood, this vehicle features a robust 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine that produces a powerful 150HP, paired with a seamless CVT transmission for smooth acceleration and optimal fuel efficiency. The Civic Sport not only delivers impressive performance but also comes equipped with a suite of advanced technological features that enhance both safety and convenience.

One of the standout features of the Honda Civic Sport is its Smart device mirroring capability. This allows you to effortlessly control your smartphone through the vehicles infotainment system, keeping your eyes on the road while accessing your favorite apps.

Safety is a top priority in the Honda Civic Sport. The Forward collision mitigation system is designed to detect potential collisions and activate preventive measures, ensuring the protection of you and your passengers. Additionally, the Front pedestrian impact prevention feature constantly monitors the road for pedestrians, providing an added layer of security to avoid accidents.

Long drives are now more enjoyable thanks to the Hands-on steering assist/lane centering feature, which maintains a safe distance from other vehicles while keeping you centered in your lane. The Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go feature further reduces stress in heavy traffic by automatically adjusting your speed and stopping when necessary.

Moreover, the Lane departure prevention system actively keeps you within your lane, while the Brake assist technology provides critical support during sudden stops. The Rear camera enhances visibility when reversing, allowing you to avoid obstacles effortlessly.

For added convenience, the Keyfob vehicle start control lets you remotely start your engine so that your car is comfortable and ready when you are. With the Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls, maintaining your desired speed is a breeze, minimizing driver fatigue on long journeys.

In conclusion, the Certified 2025 Honda Civic Sport is the perfect blend of safety, technology, and performance. Don t miss out on this opportunity to own a reliable, efficient, and stylish vehicle that will elevate your driving experience to new heights! Act fast before this deal is gone!

description:
Introducing the **2025 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport** with the ***Option Group 01*** package, an exceptional vehicle that seamlessly merges efficiency, cutting-edge technology, and robust safety features tailored for modern drivers. Under the hood, the Elantra Hybrid boasts a powerful KAPPA 1.6L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine paired with a 6-speed EcoShift DCT auto-shift manual transmission, delivering an impressive 104HP for a smooth and exhilarating driving experience.

One of the standout highlights of the Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport is its **Smart Device Mirroring** feature. This innovative technology allows you to effortlessly control your smartphone through the vehicles infotainment system, enhancing convenience while ensuring you stay focused on the road. The integration of your smart device not only boosts safety but also turns every drive into an enjoyable experience.

Safety is paramount in the Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport, accentuated by the **Hands-on Steering Assist/Lane Centering** feature. This intelligent system acts as your driving companion, ensuring you maintain a safe distance from other vehicles while helping you stay centered in your lane. Ideal for long road trips, it significantly reduces driver fatigue and elevates overall safety.

In busy urban settings, the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** system stands out. This advanced feature continuously monitors the road ahead, identifying pedestrians and taking proactive measures to prevent potential collisions, offering peace of mind in crowded environments.

Another crucial safety enhancement is **Brake Assist**, which provides increased stopping power during emergency situations. This feature detects panic braking and applies maximum braking force, ensuring you can stop quickly and safely. Additionally, the **Forward Collision Mitigation** system activates various safety measures to prepare your vehicle for potential collisions, helping to minimize impact.

The **Driver Attention Monitor** further ensures that you stay alert on your journey by notifying you if it detects signs of drowsiness or inattention. Coupled with **Traffic Sign Information and Automatic Speed Limit Assist**, you ll always be aware of speed limits, helping you avoid costly speeding tickets.

Convenience is at your fingertips with the **Proximity Key with Keyless Entry and Push Button Start**, allowing you to unlock and start your vehicle without the hassle of searching for keys. And with **Lane Departure Prevention**, your vehicle will assist in keeping you safely within your lane.

The **2025 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport** with the ***Option Group 01*** package is a remarkable choice, offering an ideal blend of advanced technology, essential safety features, and hybrid efficiency. Experience the future of driving with the Elantra Hybrid today!

description:
Introducing the **Certified 2025 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport** featuring the ***Option Group 01*** package. This remarkable hybrid sedan is the epitome of modern driving, seamlessly blending efficiency, innovative technology, and comprehensive safety features for an unparalleled driving experience.

The heart of the **Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport** is its cutting-edge KAPPA 1.6L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, which churns out an impressive 104HP. Paired with a 6-speed EcoShift DCT auto-shift manual transmission, this vehicle promises smooth acceleration and an engaging driving experience that is both dynamic and fuel-efficient.

One of the standout features of the **Elantra Hybrid** is its **Smart Device Mirroring** capability. This technology allows you to connect your smartphone to the vehicle s infotainment system effortlessly, enabling you to manage calls, music, and navigation without taking your eyes off the road. This integration prioritizes both convenience and safety, making every drive a breeze.

Safety is paramount in the **Elantra Hybrid**, equipped with advanced systems like **Hands-on Steering Assist/Lane Centering**, which helps maintain your vehicles position within its lane with minimal input. Additionally, the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** system actively monitors the road ahead, taking preemptive actions to avoid potential collisions with pedestrians.

In times of urgency, the **Brake Assist** technology enhances your stopping power, ensuring you can react swiftly in critical situations. The vehicle also incorporates **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls**, allowing you to maintain a set speed and reduce driver fatigue during long drives.

For added safety, the **Forward Collision Mitigation** system prepares you for any potential hazards on the road, while the **Driver Attention Monitor** keeps you alert, helping to prevent distractions. The **Traffic Sign Information with Automatic Speed Limit Assist** feature is particularly helpful, displaying important speed limit information and adjusting your vehicles speed to help you stay compliant.

Convenience is further enhanced with the **Proximity Key with Keyless Entry and Push Button Start**, allowing for easy access without fumbling for keys. The **Lane Departure Prevention** system adds another layer of security, ensuring your vehicle remains safely within its lane.

In conclusion, the **Certified 2025 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid SEL Sport** with the ***Option Group 01*** package is a superb choice for anyone seeking a stylish, efficient, and safe driving experience. Embrace the future of driving with the Elantra Hybrid, where elegance meets technology!

This 2014 Land Rover Range Rover Supercharged is the resulting masterpiece of Land Rover s transition into the luxury SUV market. description:
Discover the exceptional 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLK GLK 350 - a sophisticated and versatile SUV that blends exhilarating performance with uncompromising luxury. This meticulously maintained vehicle boasts a striking white exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior that exudes refinement and comfort.

Equipped with a powerful 3.5L V6 DOHC 24V engine and a smooth 7-Speed Automatic transmission, the GLK 350 delivers an exceptional driving experience, with impressive fuel efficiency of 19 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway. Standout features include:

. Speed-sensing steering
. Traction control
. ABS brakes
. Anti-whiplash front head restraints
. Child-Seat-Sensing Airbag
. Dual front impact airbags
. Dual front side impact airbags
. Emergency communication system: mbrace2
. Knee airbag
. Low tire pressure warning
. Occupant sensing airbag
. Overhead airbag
. Brake assist
. Electronic Stability Control

This well-equipped GLK 350 also boasts a premium audio system with COMAND? technology, dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable front seats with memory settings, and a wealth of other thoughtful amenities that enhance both comfort and convenience.

Meticulously maintained and backed by a comprehensive vehicle history report, this 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLK 350 represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned luxury SUV market. With its blend of style, performance, and advanced safety features, it's the perfect choice for discerning drivers seeking a truly exceptional driving experience.

We invite you to experience the exceptional quality and craftsmanship of this 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLK 350 for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the unparalleled joy of Mercedes-Benz ownership.

description:
Introducing the 2015 Ford F-150 XLT - a powerful and reliable truck that will exceed all of your expectations. This stunning vehicle is built to handle any job, whether it's towing heavy loads or navigating tough terrain. With its spacious interior and sleek exterior design, the F-150 XLT is the perfect combination of style and functionality.

Under the hood, you'll find a robust 3.5L V6 engine that delivers impressive performance and fuel efficiency. The XLT also comes equipped with advanced technology features such as a touchscreen display, Bluetooth connectivity, and a backup camera, making every drive a comfortable and enjoyable experience.

But that's not all - the 2015 F-150 XLT is also packed with safety features to give you peace of mind on the road. From its strong steel frame to its advanced airbag system, this truck has been designed to keep you and your passengers safe.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional truck. Visit our dealership today and take the 2015 Ford F-150 XLT for a test drive. With its exceptional performance, advanced technology, and top-notch safety features, this truck is the perfect choice for anyone in need of a reliable and versatile vehicle. Don't wait any longer, upgrade to the 2015 F-150 XLT and experience the ultimate driving experience.

description:
This Jeep Wrangler in Yellow is a versatile and capable vehicle that blends rugged design with modern amenities. With a powerful 3.6-liter V6 engine under the hood, this 4WD SUV is ready to tackle various terrains with confidence. The Wrangler features four doors, making it convenient for passengers to enter and exit the vehicle.

Inside the Wrangler, you'll find a well-appointed cabin with comfortable seating for the driver and front passenger. The active seat belt system ensures safety for all occupants. The left-hand drive steering layout makes driving intuitive and easy. This model comes with manual seat belts, adding an extra layer of safety for everyone on board.

Safety features in this Wrangler include hydraulic braking system, direct tire pressure monitoring system, manual seat belts, and daytime running lights, enhancing visibility on the road. The vehicle also comes equipped with ABS and electronic stability control to provide added security during your journeys.

This Jeep Wrangler is designed for adventure and practicality, offering a balance of off-road capability and on-road comfort. Transform your driving experiences with this Sport trim Wrangler, exclusively available at Mercedes-Benz of Farmington.

description:
=== Disclaimer ===

*Fair and Transparent Sales Policy*
At Autohon, we operate under a 'First Come, First Serve' policy to ensure fairness for all customers. Please note that our vehicles may have minor cosmetic imperfections, such as road chips, scratches, or wheel scuffs, and normal wear and tear should be anticipated depending on the vehicle's age. To avoid disappointment, we recommend verifying vehicle availability prior to your visit.

*Pricing Transparency*
All advertised prices exclude government fees, taxes, finance charges, dealer document processing fees, and any emissions testing charges. We also offer additional options, including a Lo Jack, Extended Warranty, and Tesla Convenience Package (On Tesla's Only), each priced up to $1999. While we strive for accuracy in our posted prices, typographical errors may occur. In the event of an incorrect price due to such errors, the dealership is only responsible for providing the correct price once identified.

*Vehicle Condition and Verification*
We make every effort to provide accurate, up-to-date information; however, it is your responsibility to verify that all details are correct before completing your purchase. Vehicle images and descriptions on our website are provided by our suppliers, and actual vehicles may differ slightly from their specifications.While every reasonable effort is made to ensure the accuracy of this information, we are not responsible for any errors or omissions contained on these pages. Images, prices, and options shown, including vehicle color, trim, options, pricing and other specifications are subject to availability, incentive offerings, current pricing and credit worthiness. Images are for illustrative purposes only.

*WARNING:* Operating, servicing and maintaining a passenger vehicle can expose you to chemicals including engine exhaust, carbon monoxide, phthalates, and lead, which are known to the State of California to cause cancer and birth defects or other reproductive harm. To minimize exposure, avoid breathing exhaust, do not idle the engine except as necessary, service your vehicle in a well-ventilated area and wear gloves or wash your hands frequently when servicing your vehicle. description: Discover the rugged versatility of this 2016 Ford F-150 XL, a dependable pickup truck designed to handle both work and leisure with ease. Featuring a striking Magnetic exterior complemented by a comfortable Gray interior, this used F-150 boasts 96,127 miles of proven performance. Powered by a 3.5-liter V6 engine with 282 horsepower and 253 lb-ft of torque, it offers a natural aspiration that delivers reliable power and efficiency. The 6-speed automatic electronic transmission ensures smooth shifting, while the 4WD drivetrain provides exceptional capability on challenging terrains. This model is equipped with a tow package, making it ideal for hauling trailers, boats, or heavy loads, and is perfect for those seeking a durable, versatile pickup with a spacious four-door configuration and seating for six. This Ford F-150 combines practical features with impressive performance, making it a compelling choice for drivers who need both utility and comfort. Its combination of city MPG of 17 and highway MPG of 23 ensures efficiency without sacrificing power. The vehicle's robust construction and standard Gray exterior give it a classic, no-nonsense look, while the Gray interior offers durability and comfort. Whether tackling tough jobs or enjoying weekend adventures, this truck's well-rounded profile makes it an excellent investment for those who demand reliability and capability in their vehicle. 2016 Ford F-150 Safety and Security Features This F-150 prioritizes safety with essential features such as 4-wheel ABS, which provides enhanced stopping power and stability under various driving conditions. It also comes equipped with emergency braking preparation, giving added confidence in sudden stop situations, and an electronic parking brake that simplifies parking and adds security when the vehicle is parked. 2016 Ford F-150 Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment is covered with a sound system that includes six total speakers, offering clear and immersive audio for all passengers. This feature ensures that drivers and their crews can enjoy their favorite music or radio broadcasts during every journey, enhancing the overall driving experience. 2016 Ford F-150 Performance Features Performance-wise, this F-150 features an electronic hi-lo 4WD selector, allowing drivers to switch between high and low gear ranges for optimal traction and control in diverse driving conditions. Its 4WD system is part-time, giving flexibility to engage or disengage the four-wheel drive as needed, ensuring that the truck performs confidently whether on the highway or off-road.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2016 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300, a masterpiece of German engineering that blends style, performance, and unparalleled luxury. This stunning vehicle, finished in a sleek White exterior, is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence.

Multimedia Package
Premium 1 Package
Sport Package
SiriusXM Satellite Radio
KEYLESS GO®
Panorama Sunroof
Blind Spot Assist
Surround Light Mirror Mounted Entry Lamps
Artico Instrument Cluster
COMAND® Navigation & Voice Control
Navigation Map Updates Included For 3 Years
SiriusXM Traffic and Weather Services
Wheels: 18 AMG® Black 5-Spoke Alloy

Powered by a robust 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine and paired with a responsive 7G-TRONIC PLUS 7-Speed Automatic transmission, this C 300 delivers an exhilarating driving experience with an impressive 25 city / 34 highway MPG. The rear-wheel-drive configuration provides exceptional handling and control, ensuring a thrilling journey every time you get behind the wheel.

The interior of this C-Class is a true sanctuary, with premium Artico upholstery, a spacious and well-appointed cabin, and a host of advanced features that cater to your every need. The Multimedia Package and COMAND® Navigation system seamlessly integrate technology, keeping you connected and entertained. The Panorama Sunroof and Blind Spot Assist further enhance the driving experience, providing both a sense of openness and added peace of mind.

This C 300 is a true testament to Mercedes-Benz's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. With its stunning design, impressive performance, and exceptional features, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the best. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that this C-Class will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

Discover the Pinnacle of Spacious Luxury with the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban LT

This stunning 2017 Chevrolet Suburban LT is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. With its sleek silver exterior and a wealth of premium features, this Suburban is poised to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

. Clean Autocheck/Vehicle History Report

The Suburban LT comes equipped with the impressive EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, delivering a potent performance while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency with 16 city/23 highway MPG. Elevate your journeys with the SUN, ENTERTAINMENT AND DESTINATIONS PACKAGE, featuring a power sunroof, rear-seat DVD entertainment system, and Chevrolet MyLink navigation. The TEXAS EDITION PACKAGE adds a host of convenience and luxury enhancements, including a hands-free liftgate, wireless charging, and a heated steering wheel.

Towing and hauling are a breeze with the MAX TRAILERING PACKAGE, which includes a trailer brake controller and a 3.42 rear axle ratio. Enjoy the smooth ride and confident handling provided by the Premium Smooth Ride Suspension Package and the Standard Suspension Package.

Step inside the spacious cabin and discover the comfort and convenience of features like dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, and a Bose premium audio system. The leather-appointed seating, heated front seats, and power driver's seat ensure a truly luxurious driving experience.

Safety is a top priority, with advanced features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert keeping you and your loved ones secure. The Suburban's impressive towing capacity and ample cargo space make it the perfect companion for your adventures, whether it's a family road trip or a weekend getaway.

Experience the pinnacle of spacious luxury with the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban LT. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true power and versatility of this remarkable vehicle.

description:
The 2017 Acura MDX 3.5L SH-AWD with Technology Package is a premium three-row luxury SUV powered by a 3.5-liter V6 engine paired with a 9-speed automatic and Acura's Super Handling All-Wheel Drive for confident performance and handling. This Technology Package adds desirable features like navigation, remote engine start, power-folding side mirrors, and a premium Acura/ELS Studio audio system for enhanced comfort and convenience. Inside, it seats up to seven with leather-trimmed seating and includes modern safety tech such as adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, and lane-departure warning. Exterior upgrades like 20-inch alloy wheels and LED lighting complement its refined, sporty appearance. With a blend of performance, technology, and family-friendly versatility, this MDX trim delivers a well-rounded, upscale SUV experience.

Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous, multi-point inspection before its ever offered for sale because quality and safety aren't just priorities for us, they're part of our heritage. Our factory-trained technicians thoroughly examine all major systems, including the engine, transmission, brakes, suspension, tires, and electrical components, to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage, mechanical issues, and cosmetic wear, inside and out. If something doesn't meet our strict criteria, its either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind; you deserve a vehicle you can count on.
That commitment runs deep in our roots. The Jackie Cooper name has proudly served Oklahoma's automotive community since 1946. We are a third-generation, family-owned dealership group that began with my grandfather, Claude Cooper, well known as the best mechanic in Canadian County. He launched our family's journey in the car business by purchasing his first franchise, an Oldsmobile dealership in Yukon, from the local funeral director who, in true small-town fashion, sold cars and conducted funerals in the same building. Yes, really.
After Claude, my father Jackie Cooper took the reins, and our family's dedication to service, honesty, and relationships only grew stronger. We've been part of countless Oklahomans' lives for nearly 80 years, he
If you would like to schedule a VIP appt, please feel free to contact us at 918.806.8548 Helping generations find dependable vehicles and standing by every customer long after the sale.
Like any business, we're not perfect but when we fall short, we make it right. The lessons passed down from my grandfather and father still guide us today: always do the right thing, treat people with respect, and earn trust every single day.
At Jackie Cooper, you're not just buying a used vehicle, you're joining a legacy built on integrity, quality, and care.

description:
Discover the power and capability of this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT. Boasting a robust 3.5L V6 EcoBoost engine, this truck delivers exceptional performance and towing capacity, making it the perfect companion for your next big adventure. Outfitted with a wealth of premium features, this F-150 is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Key highlights include:
Equipment Group 302A Luxury
GVWR: 7,000 lbs Payload Package
Max Trailer Tow Package
XLT Chrome Appearance Package
Radio: Single-CD with SiriusXM Satellite
Auxiliary Transmission Oil Cooler
Power-Adjustable Pedals
Upgraded Front Stabilizer Bar
Remote Start System
Power Moonroof

This F-150 is more than just a workhorse it's a sophisticated and well-equipped truck that can handle all your needs. With the Max Trailer Tow Package, you'll enjoy a maximum towing capacity of up to 12,200 lbs, making it a breeze to haul your boat, camper, or heavy-duty equipment. The Pro Trailer Backup Assist and Integrated Trailer Brake Controller further enhance your towing experience, giving you greater control and confidence on the road.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a wealth of comfort and convenience features. The SYNC 3 infotainment system with an 8-inch touchscreen provides seamless connectivity, while the 10-way power-adjustable front seats and heated front seats ensure a comfortable ride. The power-sliding rear window and power-adjustable pedals add to the overall versatility, allowing you to customize the cabin to your liking.

Exterior highlights include the XLT Chrome Appearance Package, which adds a touch of sophistication with chrome accents on the grille, door handles, and tailgate. The 18-inch chrome-like PVD wheels and LED box lighting further enhance the truck's stylish presence.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or embarking on your next outdoor adventure, this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT is ready to take on the challenge. Experience the perfect blend of power, capability, and premium features. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can elevate your driving experience.

description: The 2017 INFINITI Q50 3.0t Premium is a stunning vehicle that delivers a blend of luxury, performance, and technology. This vehicle is powered by a robust 3L V-6 twin turbo engine that produces an impressive 300HP, paired with a smooth 7-speed automatic transmission. The Q50 is designed for those who appreciate a thrilling driving experience without compromising on comfort and style. One of the standout features of the Q50 is the **brake assist** system, which enhances safety by automatically boosting your stopping power in emergency situations. This feature is crucial for those unexpected moments on the road. Additionally, the **cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls** makes long road trips more enjoyable by allowing drivers to maintain their desired speed effortlessly, reducing fatigue and improving fuel economy. The **touchscreen** interface in the Q50 simplifies your driving experience, allowing you to access features with just a fingertip. This intuitive system keeps you connected while minimizing distractions. Moreover, the **first-row power express open/close sunroof** offers a refreshing feel, letting you enjoy the outdoors while driving. With this sunroof, you can easily switch from a closed environment to an open one with a single touch. For those who want to control the light entering the cabin, the **first-row sunshade** provides versatility. You can adjust how much sunlight you want, keeping the interior cool or letting in natural light to brighten your drive. The **twin turbo** engine also ensures that you get the most out of your fuel, providing both power and efficiency. In terms of convenience, the **proximity key with keyless entry and push button start** feature allows you to unlock and start your vehicle without fumbling for keys. It s a game-changer for busy lifestyles. Furthermore, the **wireless audio streaming** capability lets you enjoy your favorite tunes or podcasts without the hassle of cords. Overall, the 2017 INFINITI Q50 3.0t Premium is not just a vehicle; its an experience that combines performance and luxury. With its advanced features and powerful engine, it is an excellent choice for anyone looking to elevate their daily drive. If you value style, technology, and performance, this is the car for you. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian. The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. description:
The 2019 Hyundai Santa Fe SE with the Option Group 01 is an outstanding midsize SUV that seamlessly integrates safety, comfort, and cutting-edge technology, making it a perfect fit for today s discerning drivers. This vehicle is powered by the robust Theta II 2.4L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, which delivers an impressive 185 horsepower, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission for a smooth and efficient ride.

One of the most noteworthy features of the Santa Fe SE is its **Smart Device Mirroring** capability. This innovative technology effortlessly connects your smartphone to the vehicles infotainment system, allowing you to access essential apps and information without taking your eyes off the road. This feature not only boosts convenience but also enhances safety, making it easier to stay connected on the go.

Safety is paramount in the 2019 Santa Fe SE, equipped with advanced features like **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention**. This system actively monitors your surroundings for pedestrians and projects their presence onto an interior display. In case of a potential collision, it takes preemptive action to help avoid accidents, particularly beneficial in urban settings.

The **Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Stop-Go** feature revolutionizes long drives. By maintaining a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, it automatically adjusts your speed, stopping and resuming as traffic dictates. This intelligent feature acts as a reliable co-pilot, enhancing both comfort and safety during your travels.

Emergency situations are better managed thanks to **Brake Assist**, which detects sudden braking and applies maximum stopping power, helping to avert accidents before they occur. Additionally, the **Active Blind Spot System** serves as an extra layer of security, alerting you to vehicles in your blind spots, thus facilitating safer lane changes.

The **Forward Collision Mitigation** system prepares for potential impacts, activating safety features to reduce collision severity. Complementing this is the **Driver Attention Monitor**, which tracks your driving behavior and alerts you if it detects signs of drowsiness or distraction, helping to keep you focused on the road.

Moreover, features such as **Lane Departure Prevention** and **Rear Collision Mitigation** significantly bolster the vehicle s safety profile, ensuring peace of mind for every journey.

In conclusion, the 2019 Hyundai Santa Fe SE with the Option Group 01 is a feature-rich, dependable SUV that prioritizes safety, comfort, and connectivity, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a new vehicle.

A Clean CARFAX vehicle, this Tiguan has 43,314 miles below market average, making it an excellent value for drivers across West Los Angeles, including Marina del Rey, Playa Vista, Venice, Santa Monica, Culver City, and Westchester.

With its versatile interior, advanced safety features, and AWD capability, this Tiguan SE is perfect for commuting, family trips, and weekend adventures.

Performance & Handling

All-Wheel Drive with 4-wheel independent suspension

Electronic Stability Control & Traction Control

Front and rear anti-roll bars

17-inch wide multi-spoke 2-tone alloy wheels & speed-sensing steering

Comfort & Interior Features

3rd-row seating & split-folding rear seats for flexible cargo space

Heated front comfort seats & V-Tex leatherette seating surfaces

Leather shift knob, power door mirrors & front reading lights

Technology & Connectivity

Composition Media AM/FM/HD audio system

Steering-wheel-mounted audio controls & trip computer

Compass & exterior parking camera rear

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto integration available

Safety & Driver Assistance

Forward Collision Warning with Autonomous Emergency Braking mitigation

Dual front and side impact airbags, occupant sensing & overhead airbags

Delay-off headlights & turn signal indicator mirrors

Driver vanity mirror & low tire pressure warning

Style & Convenience

Sleek Platinum Gray Metallic exterior with sporty spoiler

Fully automatic headlights

Telescoping & tilt steering wheel

Clean CARFAX
Low Miles 43,314 below market average
All-Wheel Drive for year-round traction and handling
Professionally inspected and ready for immediate delivery
Available now at Airport Marina Honda, serving West Los Angeles

Introducing the **2019 Honda Civic LX**, a certified vehicle that exemplifies a perfect blend of performance, safety, and cutting-edge technology. This model is powered by a robust 2L I-4 DOHC engine, delivering an impressive 158HP through a smooth CVT transmission, ensuring efficiency while providing an enjoyable driving experience.

Safety is paramount in the **2019 Honda Civic LX**, featuring advanced systems designed to protect you and your passengers. The **Forward Collision Mitigation** system is a standout safety feature, actively detecting potential collisions and preparing the vehicle to minimize impact. This forward-thinking technology enhances your driving confidence, allowing you to focus on the road ahead.

Another remarkable feature is the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** system, which continuously monitors the road for pedestrians. This is particularly beneficial in urban environments, helping to avoid unexpected collisions and ensuring a safer driving experience. The **Rear Camera** provides an extra layer of safety by enhancing visibility while reversing, displaying a clear image of obstacles behind you and making navigation in tight spaces a breeze.

The **Lane Departure Prevention** system further contributes to safety by automatically correcting your vehicles position, reducing the chances of unintended lane changes. Long road trips are made more enjoyable thanks to the **Adaptive Cruise Control** feature, which adjusts your speed to maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, allowing for a relaxed driving experience without constant speed monitoring.

Additionally, **Brake Assist** enhances safety by detecting sudden braking needs and applying maximum brake force when necessary, helping you avoid accidents in critical moments. description:
Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and comfort in this 2020 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited. This exceptional SUV is a true standout, offering an unparalleled driving experience that will captivate you from the moment you get behind the wheel.

2 Keys!
TRAILER TOW GROUP IV
Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat
Quadra-Trac II 4WD System
GPS Navigation
Trailer Tow Group IV
6 Speakers
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
Audio memory
HD Radio
Integrated Center Stack Radio
Radio: Uconnect 4C Nav w/8.4 Display
SiriusXM Satellite Radio

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, this Grand Cherokee delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive 18 city and 25 highway MPG. The Quadra-Trac II 4WD system ensures exceptional off-road capability, while the trailer tow package elevates its versatility, allowing you to tackle any adventure with ease.

Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and technology, with features like dual-zone automatic climate control, a power driver's seat, and a premium audio system that will elevate your driving experience. The leather-trimmed seats and heated steering wheel add an extra touch of luxury, while the 8.4-inch touchscreen display with built-in navigation and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration keep you connected and in control.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and a rearview camera ensuring you and your loved ones can travel with confidence. The Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is a true standout in its class, offering a perfect blend of power, capability, and refined sophistication.

Experience the difference for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this 2020 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is the perfect SUV to elevate your driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional performance, impressive features, and uncompromising quality. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional vehicle your own.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in the 2020 Buick Encore Preferred. This off-white SUV is a true standout, offering a remarkable driving experience and a wealth of premium features to enhance your everyday commute.

. BOUGHT, SERVICED AND TRADED AT LEACHMAN
. ONE OWNER LOCAL TRADE * CLEAN ACCIDENT HISTORY
. REMOTE VEHICLE STARTER SYSTEM
. APPLE CARPLAY & ANDROID AUTO

Powered by the efficient ECOTEC 1.4L I4 SMPI DOHC Turbocharged engine, the Encore Preferred delivers an impressive 25 city / 30 highway MPG, making it an exceptional fuel-saver. Paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Electronic with Overdrive transmission, this SUV offers a seamless and responsive driving experience.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a host of thoughtful amenities, including a Remote Vehicle Starter System and the cutting-edge Buick Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay connected and in control with the convenient steering wheel-mounted audio, Bluetooth, and cruise controls.

The Encore Preferred's spacious and well-appointed interior provides a comfortable and versatile cabin, with a 6-Speaker Audio System, Power Driver Seat, and a Rear Window Defroster to enhance your driving pleasure. Enhance your commute with the Ride & Handling Suspension, Traction Control, and 4-Wheel Disc Brakes, ensuring a smooth and confident ride.

Exterior features like the Fully Automatic Headlights, Heated Door Mirrors, and Roof Rack Rails add both style and functionality, while the Rear Parking Camera and Panic Alarm provide added peace of mind.

This one-owner Encore Preferred is a true gem, with a clean accident history and a wealth of premium features that make it an exceptional value. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance - schedule a test drive today and discover why the 2020 Buick Encore Preferred is the perfect choice for your next SUV.

description: Our sporty One Owner 2021 Volkswagen Jetta R-Line Sedan brings an athletic attitude to every drive in Platinum Gray Metallic! Motivated by a TurboCharged 1.4 Liter TSI 4 Cylinder supplying 147hp connected to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission. You'll enjoy responsive handling as well since our Front Wheel Drive sedan comes standard with an XDS cross-differential system, and you'll see nearly 39mpg on the highway. The bold good looks of our Jetta are then enhanced by an exclusive R-Line bumper and grille plus LED lighting, fog lamps, panoramic sunroof, heated power mirrors, chrome grille, and 17-inch alloy wheels. You're ready to master every mile in our R-Line cockpit that showcases V-Tex leatherette heated front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, keyless access, and push-button ignition for your comfort and convenience. For an important digital advantage, there's a 6.5-inch touchscreen that supports Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, and a four-speaker sound system. Volkswagen helps keep you out of harm's way with a backup camera, automatic braking, forward collision warning, pedestrian detection, a blind-spot monitor, rear cross-traffic alert, ABS, tire-pressure monitoring, advanced airbags, and more. Our Jetta R-Line sedan will transform your driving for the better with its German engineering! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry pick only the best of the best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82 point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety. Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians, who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality control technician, before being sent to our state of the art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack. Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance, while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top quality name brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep. Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews, and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today, and experience the difference.

description:
The 2021 Hyundai Tucson SEL is a well-maintained, all-wheel-drive compact SUV, finished in a sleek White Cream exterior with a gray cloth interior. Powered by a 2.4L I4 engine and paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, this vehicle offers smooth and efficient performance. The Tucson SEL comes equipped with a range of premium features, including a 10.25 digital display, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, SiriusXM radio, and a backup camera. For added comfort, it features heated front seats, a power-adjustable driver's seat, and a moonroof.

Safety features include forward collision warning, lane-keeping assist, blind-spot monitoring, rear cross-traffic alert, and adaptive cruise control, ensuring that you stay safe on every drive. The Tucson SEL is also equipped with a power liftgate, roof rails, and alloy wheels, enhancing both its functionality and style.

This vehicle has been serviced regularly, including oil changes, new brakes, and tire rotations. It has a clean CARFAX with no reported accidents or damage, and with 48,496 miles on the odometer, it remains in excellent condition.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of performance, style, and versatility in the 2021 Subaru Impreza Base. This compact car is designed to elevate your driving experience with its exceptional all-wheel-drive capability, fuel-efficient engine, and a host of advanced features that cater to your every need.

Tailored to your preferences, this Impreza comes equipped with the following premium upgrades:

Popular Package #3, which includes an auto-dimming mirror with compass and HomeLink, all-weather floor liners, LED-upgraded map and dome lights, and an auto-dimming exterior mirror with approach light
A convenient windshield sunshade

Beyond these thoughtful additions, the Impreza Base offers a well-rounded package that combines Subaru's renowned reliability with a host of standard features, including:

4-speaker audio system with AM/FM radio and STARLINK 6.5 multimedia system
Air conditioning and rear window defroster
Power windows, locks, and mirrors
Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
Four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering
Traction control and 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS
Dual front, side, and knee airbags, plus overhead and anti-whiplash head restraints

Slip behind the wheel of this 2021 Subaru Impreza Base, and you'll immediately appreciate its responsive 2.0L DOHC engine paired with a smooth-shifting 5-speed manual transmission. With an EPA-estimated 24 MPG in the city and 31 MPG on the highway, this all-wheel-drive compact car delivers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency to tackle your daily commute and weekend adventures with ease.

The Impreza's sleek, modern exterior is complemented by a spacious and well-appointed interior, offering ample room for passengers and cargo. Enjoy the convenience of the rearview camera, the comfort of the split-folding rear seats, and the versatility of the 60/40 layout, making it easy to accommodate your lifestyle needs.

Whether you're looking for a reliable daily driver, a versatile family car, or a spirited companion for your outdoor pursuits, the 2021 Subaru Impreza Base is an exceptional choice that will exceed your expectations. Experience the confidence and capability that Subaru is known for, and let this Impreza become your trusted partner on the road ahead.

We invite you to visit our showroom and take this remarkable Impreza for a test drive. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you discover the perfect Subaru to meet your needs. We're confident that once you experience the Impreza's exceptional performance and features, you'll be eager to make it your own.

The Tucson Value also comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Lane Keeping Assist, providing you with added peace of mind on the road.

description:
<p>Discover the 2021 Hyundai Kona SE: A Compact SUV That Marries Style, Efficiency, and Advanced Safety for the Modern Urban Driver</p>
<p>Step into the world of the 2021 Hyundai Kona SE, where sleek design meets advanced functionality. This Ultra Black beauty is tailored for those who crave a dynamic driving experience without compromising on safety or style. The 4-cylinder engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission ensures a smooth and efficient ride, making it perfect for city commutes or weekend getaways. </p>
<p>Safety is paramount with features like Lane Keeping Assist and Front Collision Mitigation, offering peace of mind on every journey. The Kona SE’s advanced Driver Monitoring system keeps you alert, while the Brake Assist and Stability Control enhance handling in diverse driving conditions. </p>
<p>Inside, the Kona SE is designed for connectivity and convenience. The Smart Device Integration and Bluetooth Connection keep you seamlessly connected, while the intuitive Steering Wheel Audio Controls offer effortless command over your entertainment. </p>
<p>With its sporty rear spoiler and all-season tires, the Kona SE not only looks the part but performs impeccably across terrains. The combination of a Rear Bench Seat and Pass-Through Rear Seat provides versatile cargo options, making it a perfect companion for both daily tasks and spontaneous adventures.</p>

description:
The 2021 Chevrolet Trailblazer FWD LT is an exceptional SUV that combines advanced safety features, modern technology, and a stylish design to enhance your driving experience. This model does not come with any additional packages, which only emphasizes the standard high-quality features it offers.

Equipped with the robust ECOTEC 1.3L I-3 gasoline direct injection engine, the Trailblazer delivers a remarkable 155 horsepower paired with a smooth Continuously Variable Transmission CVT. This powertrain not only ensures a dynamic driving experience but also promotes fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for both city commuting and long road trips.

Safety is a primary focus in the 2021 Chevrolet Trailblazer FWD LT. One of its standout features is **Forward Collision Mitigation**. This innovative system actively monitors the road ahead, detecting potential collisions and preparing the vehicle to respond, significantly reducing the risk of accidents. Additionally, the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** feature enhances safety further by tracking pedestrians and taking necessary measures to avoid potential impacts, making it perfect for urban environments.

In today s tech-savvy world, connectivity is crucial, and the Trailblazer delivers with its **Mobile Hotspot** feature. This allows you to connect multiple devices to the internet seamlessly, ensuring you can stay entertained and connected during your travels. The **Rear Camera** enhances your visibility when reversing, making parking and maneuvering in tight spaces much easier and safer.

The Trailblazer also includes **Lane Departure Prevention**, which helps keep you centered in your lane by alerting you if you start to drift and automatically applying corrective steering if needed. The **Brake Assist** feature further enhances safety by providing additional stopping power during emergency braking situations, proving that the Trailblazer is built with your safety in mind.

For added convenience on long journeys, the **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls** allows you to set and maintain a constant speed, reducing driver fatigue. The **Keyfob Engine Start Control** means you can start your vehicle remotely, so its warmed up and ready by the time you step inside.

Comfort is also prioritized with **Heated Driver and Front Passenger Seats**, providing warmth and comfort on chilly days. Overall, the 2021 Chevrolet Trailblazer FWD LT stands out as a premier choice for modern drivers seeking a reliable, safe, and connected SUV. Whether youre navigating city streets or hitting the open road, the Trailblazer is designed to elevate your driving experience.

Introducing the **2022 Ram 1500 Classic Tradesman Regular Cab 4x2 8 Box** equipped with the highly desirable **Power and Remote Entry Group** and **Quick Order Package 29B Tradesman**. This robust pickup truck is meticulously crafted to offer an exceptional combination of durability, performance, and practicality, making it an outstanding choice for both work and leisure pursuits.

At the heart of the Ram 1500 Classic is the powerful Pentastar 3.6L V-6 DOHC engine, producing an impressive 305 horsepower. Coupled with the efficient TorqueFlite 8-speed automatic transmission, this truck delivers a seamless driving experience, whether youre navigating tight city streets or cruising on the open highway.

One of the standout attributes of the Ram 1500 Classic is its **wireless connectivity**. This feature allows for effortless integration with your smartphone, enabling hands-free access to calls and messages, ensuring you stay connected while keeping your focus on the road. The interior is also designed for functionality, featuring durable **vinyl seat upholstery** that simplifies cleaning and maintenance, ideal for everyday use.

Loading and unloading cargo has never been easier thanks to the **keyfob cargo access control**. With a simple push of a button, you can unlock the cargo area without having to juggle your belongings, making it incredibly convenient. Safety is also prioritized with the inclusion of a **rear camera**, which enhances visibility when reversing, helping you avoid obstacles and hazards.

In terms of safety technology, the Ram 1500 Classic is equipped with **brake assist**, which detects rapid braking situations and applies maximum braking force to help you stop effectively. Additionally, the **cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls** makes long drives more comfortable by maintaining your selected speed with minimal effort.

The trucks modern **touchscreen interface** provides easy access to various features, ensuring an intuitive user experience. With advanced innovations such as **variable valve timing** and a **DOHC valvetrain**, you can expect optimal performance that enhances fuel efficiency while minimizing emissions.

In conclusion, the **2022 Ram 1500 Classic Tradesman Regular Cab 4x2 8 Box** featuring the **Power and Remote Entry Group** and **Quick Order Package 29B Tradesman** is a versatile and reliable pickup. With its powerful engine, advanced safety features, and user-friendly technology, this truck is perfect for anyone seeking both performance and functionality. Dont miss out on experiencing this remarkable vehicle!

description:
The 2022 Chevrolet Colorado Work Truck is a rugged and capable pickup that's ready to take on any challenge. With its powerful V6 engine, impressive fuel efficiency, and a wealth of convenient features, this Colorado is the perfect choice for both work and play.

Key highlights include:
3.6L V6 engine with 308 HP and 275 lb-ft of torque
WT Convenience Package with remote keyless entry, theft-deterrent system, cruise control, and more
OnStar and Chevrolet Connected Services capability
Remote locking tailgate
EZ-Lift and Lower tailgate
Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system with 6-speaker audio

The Colorado Work Truck is built to work hard and play hard. Its rugged construction and capable powertrain make it a workhorse that can handle heavy-duty tasks with ease. Whether you're hauling equipment, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, this Colorado has the performance and versatility to get the job done.

Inside, the Colorado offers a comfortable and well-equipped cabin. The 6-way power driver's seat and tilt steering wheel provide a customizable driving position, while the 6-speaker audio system and Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system keep you entertained on the go. The split-folding rear seat and ample storage space make it easy to accommodate both passengers and cargo.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control to help keep you and your passengers secure. The rearview camera and rear park assist make it easy to maneuver in tight spaces, while the theft-deterrent system helps protect your investment.

If you're in the market for a hardworking, versatile, and well-equipped pickup, the 2022 Chevrolet Colorado Work Truck is an excellent choice. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful features, and confident styling, this Colorado is sure to impress. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and experience the difference for yourself.

description:
The 2022 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE is an impressive vehicle that seamlessly combines efficiency, technology, and safety. This model is powered by a robust 1.8L I-4 DOHC engine, delivering a commendable 96 horsepower through its efficient CVTi-S CVT transmission, ensuring an outstanding driving experience while prioritizing fuel economy.

One of the most notable features of the Corolla Hybrid LE is its **Forward Collision Mitigation** system, a vital safety enhancement that actively monitors potential hazards ahead. This technology readies the vehicle for an impending impact, giving drivers peace of mind, especially in bustling urban environments where sudden stops are common.

Additionally, the **Hands-on Steering Assist/Lane Centering** feature transforms your driving experience, helping maintain your vehicle s position within the lane. This means you can focus more on the road ahead, minimizing the need for constant adjustments. Paired with **Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Stop-Go**, the Corolla Hybrid LE takes the stress out of long drives by automatically adjusting your speed in response to traffic conditions, coming to a complete stop when necessary.

For tech-savvy drivers, the **Smart Device Mirroring** feature offers seamless integration with your smartphone, allowing for effortless access to apps and navigation through the vehicle s infotainment system. Furthermore, the **Mobile Hotspot** capability ensures that you remain connected on the go, without using up your mobile data.

Safety remains a priority with the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** system, which continuously scans the road for pedestrians, taking proactive measures to avoid collisions. The **Lane Departure Prevention** feature further enhances safety by automatically correcting any unintended lane drift, ensuring a secure driving experience.

When reversing, the **Rear Camera** proves invaluable, providing a clear view of obstacles that may be in your path, while the **Brake Assist** feature boosts stopping power in emergency situations, enhancing overall safety and reducing the likelihood of accidents.

In conclusion, the 2022 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE is an exceptional choice for those seeking a reliable and technologically advanced hybrid vehicle. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and affordability in the 2023 Kia Rio S. This compact sedan delivers an exceptional driving experience that will elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Highlighted features include:

Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Traction control
ABS brakes
Low tire pressure warning
Electronic Stability Control
Heated door mirrors
Illuminated entry
15 steel wheels with full covers

The Rio S offers an impressive array of amenities, including air conditioning, power windows, power steering, and a 6-speaker audio system with AM/FM and MP3 capabilities. Safety is paramount, with dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and a host of advanced safety technologies to keep you and your passengers secure.

Boasting an EPA-estimated 32 MPG in the city and 41 MPG on the highway, the Rio S delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, allowing you to go further on every tank. Its 1.6L 4-cylinder engine and CVT transmission provide a smooth, responsive driving experience that adapts to your needs.

Exterior highlights include the Aurora Black paint, complemented by the sleek, modern design that turns heads wherever you go. Inside, the Woven & Tricot Cloth Seat Trim offers comfort and style, while the split-folding rear seat provides versatility to accommodate your cargo needs.

Experience the perfect balance of practicality, performance, and style in the 2023 Kia Rio S. This vehicle is a testament to Kia's commitment to delivering exceptional value, and it's waiting for you to take it home.

Comes with a Lifetime Powertrain Warranty at no extra charge on qualifying new vehicles. Coverage that lasts as long as you own the vehicle with no mileage limits. See dealer for full details and exclusions.

Step into the next level of driving excellence with this 2023 Nissan Rogue SV, now available at Sierra Nissan of Duarte. This stunning SUV, finished in a sophisticated Gun Metallic exterior, perfectly balances modern style with the rugged capability you expect from a leader in the crossover segment. With only 57,638 miles, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide its next owner with years of reliable, high-tech performance.

The interior is a sanctuary of comfort and utility, featuring a spacious Charcoal interior that remains in excellent condition. While the SV trim offers plush seating for five, the cabin is designed with the driver in mind, boasting an 8-way power drivers seat with 2-way lumbar support to ensure comfort on even the longest commutes. The 2023 Rogue is powered by an innovative 1.5L VC-Turbo engine, delivering a class-leading 201 horsepower and 225 lb-ft of torque, giving you punchy acceleration without sacrificing fuel efficiency.


Safety is the cornerstone of the Rogue experience. This vehicle comes equipped with the Nissan Safety Shield 360 suite, offering the most standard safety features in its class. Youll drive with total peace of mind thanks to:

Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection

Blind Spot Warning and Rear Cross Traffic Alert

Lane Departure Warning and Rear Automatic Braking

High Beam Assist


At Sierra Nissan of Duarte, located conveniently at 1125 Central Ave, we pride ourselves on transparency. This Rogue has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection by our factory-trained technicians to ensure every system from the Intelligent Key with push-button start to the dual-zone automatic climate control functions perfectly. For those who value connectivity, the 8-inch NissanConnect touchscreen with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps your world at your fingertips.

Whether you're loading up for a weekend getaway using the massive 74.1 cubic feet of max cargo space or navigating the daily 210 freeway commute, this Gun Metallic Rogue SV is the ideal companion. Don't miss your chance to own one of the safest and most versatile SUVs on the market. Visit us today at Sierra Nissan of Duarte to experience this 2023 Rogue firsthand. Our dedicated team is ready to provide a stress-free buying experience and help you drive home in this exceptional vehicle.
