description:
The 2023 Hyundai Kona N Line, featuring the **Cargo Package** and **Option Group 01**, is a remarkable compact SUV that combines spirited performance with cutting-edge technology and advanced safety features. At the heart of the Kona N Line is the dynamic Gamma 1.6L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, which produces an impressive 195 horsepower paired with a smooth 7-speed auto-shift manual transmission. This powerful combination ensures an exhilarating driving experience, whether youre navigating city streets or cruising on the highway.

The **Cargo Package** enhances the vehicle s practicality by providing ample storage solutions, making it perfect for spontaneous getaways or everyday errands. Meanwhile, **Option Group 01** offers essential features at no extra cost, ensuring that your journeys are both enjoyable and economical.

Safety is a top priority in the Kona N Line, which is equipped with a suite of advanced safety technologies. The **Smart device mirroring** feature allows for seamless smartphone integration with the vehicles infotainment system, enabling easy access to navigation and entertainment while keeping your focus on the road. The **Hands-on steering assist/lane centering** technology adds another layer of safety by helping you maintain a secure position in your lane and a safe distance from surrounding vehicles.

One of the standout features is the **Front pedestrian impact prevention** system, which actively monitors the road for pedestrians and takes preventive measures to avoid collisions. Coupled with **Brake assist**, which enhances stopping power during emergencies, the Kona N Line ensures peace of mind in every drive.

Long drives become more enjoyable with features like **Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls**, allowing you to effortlessly maintain your desired speed. The **Heated driver and front passenger seats** provide added comfort on chilly days, ensuring a cozy ride for everyone.

Moreover, the **Forward collision mitigation** system prepares the vehicle for potential impacts, enhancing safety further. The **Driver attention monitor** keeps an eye on your alertness and provides warnings if drowsiness is detected. Finally, the **Proximity key with keyless entry and push button start** simplifies access to your vehicle, while the **Lane departure prevention** feature helps correct unintended lane drift.

In summary, the 2023 Hyundai Kona N Line is an exceptional compact SUV that excels in performance, safety, and technology. With its innovative features and comfortable ride, the Kona N Line is ready to elevate your driving experience!

description:
Introducing the 2024 Toyota Corolla SE, a compact sedan that seamlessly blends modern technology and safety features, ensuring an unparalleled driving experience. With its impressive suite of innovations, the Corolla SE stands out in the automotive landscape.

One of the standout features of the Corolla SE is its **Hands-on steering assist/lane centering** system. This technology allows you to set your speed while maintaining a safe distance from other vehicles, all while effortlessly keeping you centered in your lane. Forget the stress of road trips this feature acts as your co-pilot, giving you peace of mind on long journeys.

Safety is a top priority in the 2024 Toyota Corolla SE, exemplified by its **Front pedestrian impact prevention** system. This advanced feature continuously monitors the surroundings, detecting pedestrians and taking proactive steps to prevent potential collisions. It s an assurance that your vehicle is designed to protect both you and pedestrians alike.

The **Automatic curve slowdown cruise control** is another innovative aspect of the Corolla SE. Utilizing GPS technology, this system adjusts your speed for curves and hills, minimizing fatigue and enhancing fuel efficiency. You can enjoy your travels without the constant need to adjust your speed, making it a remarkable feature for long-distance driving.

Stay connected on the go with the Corolla SEs **Mobile hotspot** capability. This feature allows you to connect your devices to the internet without using up your mobile data, making it ideal for those who need to stay connected while traveling.

To further enhance safety, the Corolla SE includes a **Rear camera** that provides a clear view of obstacles behind you, along with **Lane departure prevention** technology that helps ensure you stay in your lane. This combination of features creates a safer driving environment for you and those around you.

Additionally, the **Adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go** feature is a game-changer. It not only adjusts your speed to match the vehicle ahead but also brings you to a complete stop when necessary, resuming speed as traffic moves. Coupled with **Brake assist**, this ensures you have the stopping power needed in urgent situations.

Lastly, with **Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls**, maintaining your desired speed has never been easier.

Overall, the 2024 Toyota Corolla SE is a perfect blend of cutting-edge technology and essential safety features, making it the ideal vehicle for both daily commutes and road trips. Experience the future of driving with the Corolla SE today!

This Tacoma is powered by Toyota's famously durable engine equipped with a timing chain (not a belt) designed to last the lifetime of the motor. These trucks are widely known to run 600,000 700,000 miles with proper maintenance, and this one is just getting started.



The drivetrain, suspension, and overall feel reflect a truck that has lived an easy life. No rattles, no excuses just solid, dependable Toyota engineering from the era when these trucks were built to last forever.







Condition



Finding a 2000 Tacoma with this mileage and condition is extremely rare. The paint presents well, the interior is clean and unmolested, and everything functions as it should. It drives exactly how you'd hope an ultra-low-mile Tacoma would smooth, confident, and ready for daily use or long-term ownership.






Perfect For

Daily driver

Anyone who wants a truck that will outlast modern alternatives







Bottom Line



This is not your average used Tacoma. It's a low-mile, properly maintained, SR5 Extended Cab that showcases why these trucks have such a legendary reputation. Trucks like this simply do not come around often, especially in this condition.



If you've been waiting for the one, this is it.

===== = 2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab Pickup - Now Available at Siry Motors in San Diego, CA ======

Look no further than the *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab Pickup*, now available at *Siry Motors* in San Diego, California. Whether you re hauling heavy loads, heading to a job site, or simply cruising around San Diego, this Silverado is the perfect companion for all your driving needs.

===== Performance and Power: V8 6.0 Liter Engine =====

Under the hood of the *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab* lies a mighty *V8 6.0 Liter engine*, delivering the power and performance you need for any task. This powerhouse engine ensures you can tow, haul, and drive with confidence, whether you re transporting equipment or embarking on a weekend adventure. Paired with an automatic transmission, the Silverado offers smooth and effortless driving, making it a reliable choice for both experienced truck owners and first-time buyers.

===== Utility and Functionality: Built for the Hardest Jobs =====

The *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD* is designed with utility in mind. Its *utility body* provides ample space for tools, equipment, and supplies, making it an ideal choice for contractors, landscapers, and anyone in need of a dependable workhorse. The *8-foot bed* offers plenty of room for larger items, while the *towing package* ensures you can easily haul trailers, boats, or other heavy loads with ease.

===== Comfort and Convenience: A Driver-Focused Cabin =====

Step inside the *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab* and you ll find a comfortable and well-equipped cabin designed with the driver in mind. With features like *air conditioning*, *cruise control*, and a *tilt wheel*, every drive is a breeze. The *power windows* and *power door locks* add convenience, while the *AM/FM stereo*, *cassette player*, and *CD/MP3 (Single Disc)* provide entertainment for your journeys across San Diego and beyond.

===== Safety Features: Peace of Mind on Every Drive =====

Safety is a top priority in the *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD*. Equipped with *ABS (4-wheel)* and *dual airbags*, this truck is designed to keep you and your passengers protected on the road. Whether you re navigating busy city streets or cruising down the highway, you can drive with confidence knowing your Silverado is built to handle it all.

===== Stylish and Practical Design: Premium Wheels and Running Boards =====

The *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab* combines rugged functionality with stylish design elements. The *premium wheels* not only enhance the truck s appearance but also provide a smooth and stable ride. The addition of *running boards* makes it easy to get in and out of the cab, adding an extra layer of practicality to this already impressive vehicle.

===== Why Choose the 2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD? =====

The *2004 Chevrolet Silverado 2500 HD Regular Cab Pickup* is more than just a truck - it s a reliable partner for all your driving needs. From its powerful V8 engine to its spacious utility body and towing capabilities, this truck is built to handle whatever comes its way. Whether you re a business owner in need of a dependable work vehicle or an individual looking for a versatile and durable pickup, the Silverado is the perfect choice.

description:
Introducing the powerful and stylish 2006 Nissan 350Z, equipped with a 3L NA V6 double overhead cam (DOHC) 24V engine. This sleek sports car boasts a smooth and responsive ride, perfect for thrill-seekers and car enthusiasts alike. With its striking exterior design and spacious interior, the 350Z is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

But it's not just about looks with this beauty. The 3L NA V6 DOHC 24V engine delivers an impressive 287 horsepower and 274 lb-ft of torque, giving you the ultimate driving experience. Plus, with only 68,000 miles on the odometer, this 350Z has plenty of life left to offer.

Step inside and you'll be greeted with a well-maintained interior, featuring comfortable leather seats and modern amenities such as power windows, locks, and mirrors. The 350Z also comes equipped with a premium sound system for all your music needs.

Safety is also a top priority with the 2006 Nissan 350Z. With features like stability control, traction control, and multiple airbags, you can feel confident and secure behind the wheel.

Don't miss your chance to own this impressive 2006 Nissan 350Z with a 3L NA V6 DOHC 24V engine. With its combination of style, performance, and reliability, this car is a steal at its price. So come take a test drive and experience the thrill of driving a true sports car. Contact us today to schedule a viewing.

description:
Introducing the 2012 Acura MDX SH-AWD a luxurious and powerful SUV that delivers an unparalleled driving experience. This stunning vehicle boasts a spacious interior, advanced technology, and superior performance, making it the perfect choice for anyone seeking a premium SUV.

Step inside the 2012 MDX and you'll be greeted by a refined and comfortable cabin, complete with plush leather seats and wood grain accents. With seating for up to seven passengers, this SUV is perfect for both daily commutes and family road trips. Plus, with its ample cargo space, you'll have no problem fitting all your gear for any adventure.

But the 2012 MDX is more than just a pretty face. Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 3.7L V6 engine, delivering 300 horsepower and 270 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth and responsive 6-speed automatic transmission, this SUV offers a dynamic and exhilarating ride. And with the SH-AWD (Super Handling All-Wheel Drive) system, you'll have enhanced traction and control on any road surface.

Equipped with advanced technology, the 2012 MDX offers convenience and connectivity at your fingertips. With features like Bluetooth connectivity, a premium audio system, and a navigation system, you'll have everything you need for a seamless and enjoyable driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority in the 2012 MDX, with features like a rearview camera, adaptive cruise control, and blind spot detection. You can drive with confidence knowing that this SUV has your back on the road.

description: Venza has 87000 miles her. Changed the oil every 9-10 thousand miles with Moble1 with Toyota filter. Other than oil, brakes and battery(new last August) never had a mechanical problem with her. I was gonna replace the plugs and coils but can't reach the back side of engine so you'd get that stuff too. The later pictures show it without the bra and the last one shows a couple scratches, the worst it has. Has a few light ones here and there but it's a 8-9 outa 10 if you'd ask me. The seats have neoprene covers on them that are a year or so old, too difficult to take off so I didn't want to take a picture with them off but they've had covers on them since we bought it used in 2015. I also installed a front and rear facing camera that'll record. The tires are around 4 year old but probably still have half there life left. We bought a new 4Runner, our retirement car, so that's the only reason for selling her. She's ALWAYS been a great car for us and it's a Toyota so she'll give you plenty of more miles. I know the pictures aren't great but it's raining.

This F-150 XLT also boasts a wealth of premium features, including the Equipment Group 301A Mid, GVWR: 6,350 lbs Payload Package, Trailer Tow Package, and the XLT Sport Appearance Package. These packages deliver a host of desirable amenities, such as a leather-wrapped steering wheel, power driver's seat with lumbar support, auto-dimming rearview mirror, and a rear-view camera with dynamic hitch assist.

The exterior of this F-150 XLT is finished in a sleek White color, complemented by the unique sport appearance features, including body-color door and tailgate handles, a black billet-style grille, and 18-inch machined-aluminum wheels. Inside, the cabin offers a comfortable and well-appointed environment, with premium cloth upholstery, a 4.2-inch productivity screen, and a 110V/400W outlet for your convenience.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs, towing a trailer, or simply seeking a capable and well-equipped daily driver, this 2015 Ford F-150 XLT is an exceptional choice. AutoNation Acura South Bay has this beautiful and well cared for ONE OWNER, 2015 BMW X5 xDrive35d and here is what makes it AWESOME! Torque Monster This thing has 413 lb-ft of torque available pretty much as soon as you wantat just about 1,500 rpm. That means when you stomp the gas, you feel a shove back in your seat. Diesel Efficiency King For a luxury SUV that weighs nearly 5,000 lbs, it still does ~24 mpg city / 31 mpg highway / ~27 mpg combined . Thats way better than its gas-powered siblings. Range That Keeps Going Large fuel tank (about 22.4 gallons ) + good highway mpg = you can drive for 650+ miles without needing to refuel if you keep it chill. Minimal stops, more road trip vibes. Luxury + Utility Combo You get that high-end BMW feelnice finishes, solid engineering, luxury touches and the utility of an SUV. Plenty of room for people or cargo, solid towing capacity, all-wheel drive, etc. Strong Performer 255 horsepower doesnt sound insane up top, but with that torque low in the revs, passing, merging, climbing hills all feel strong. Ride Quality : The X5 xDrive35d offers a firm yet comfortable ride, with adaptive suspension options enhancing handling dynamics. Interior Comfort : High-quality materials and sound insulation contribute to a quiet and luxurious cabin environment.

description:
The 2015 Toyota Prius Four is a remarkable hybrid vehicle that seamlessly combines eco-friendliness with cutting-edge technology features. This model is packed with enhancements that focus on safety, comfort, and driving pleasure, making it a perfect choice for environmentally conscious consumers.

One of the standout features of the Prius Four is its Rear Camera, which provides a clear view of obstacles behind the vehicle, serving as an extra set of eyes for added safety while reversing. Moreover, the Brake Assist feature is essential for detecting sudden braking scenarios and amplifying stopping power, crucial for preventing potential accidents.

For tech-savvy drivers, the Selective Internet Access allows for tailored updates on sports scores, weather, and local news, ensuring you stay connected even while on the move. Additionally, the Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls makes long journeys less stressful by maintaining your desired speed effortlessly, which also enhances overall fuel efficiency.

Navigating unfamiliar roads is easy with the Voice Activated Integrated Navigation System. This hands-free feature lets you set your destination just by speaking, eliminating the hassle of cumbersome maps. On chilly days, the Heated Driver and Front Passenger Seats provide immediate warmth, ensuring comfort regardless of the weather conditions outside.

Inside the cabin, the Prius Four features Leatherette Seat Upholstery, which combines style with easy maintenance. The Touchscreen interface simplifies access to various features, making your driving experience user-friendly. Comfort is paramount in the Prius Four, with features like the Power Reclining Driver Seat and multiple Power Driver Seat Adjustments allowing you to find the perfect seating position for an enjoyable drive.

Under the hood, the Prius Four is powered by an Inline 4-cylinder engine equipped with Variable Valve Timing, enhancing both performance and fuel efficiency. Its DOHC configuration contributes to improved power delivery, ensuring every drive is a pleasure.

In conclusion, the 2015 Toyota Prius Four represents a fantastic blend of technology, safety, and comfort, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a reliable and efficient hybrid vehicle. With its impressive features and eco-friendly performance, the Prius Four is designed for the modern driver who values sustainability and innovation. Experience the future of driving with the Prius Four!

description:
The 2016 Volkswagen Passat 1.8T SE has seen a price drop of $-505 recently, making it an opportune time to act if youre in the market for a stylish, reliable sedan. With its blend of cutting-edge technology and safety features, the Passat is not just a vehicle; it s an experience that enhances your daily drive.

Equipped with a robust 1.8L I-4 gasoline engine that delivers 170HP paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, the Passat promises a spirited yet efficient ride. One of its standout features is the *Smart device mirroring*, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone with the vehicle s infotainment system. This feature enhances safety and convenience, enabling you to access essential apps without diverting your attention from the road.

Safety is a priority in the Passat, as evidenced by its *Forward collision mitigation* system. This advanced technology actively monitors your surroundings for potential collisions and prepares the vehicle to react, ensuring you and your passengers are protected. The *Rear camera* also adds a layer of security, offering enhanced visibility of obstacles while reversing, making it easier to navigate tight spaces.

For those longer journeys, the *Adaptive cruise control* takes away the stress of maintaining speed and distance from the vehicle ahead, allowing for a more relaxed driving experience. Coupled with *Brake assist*, which boosts braking power in emergencies, you can drive with confidence knowing that your safety is a top priority.

Comfort is another key aspect of the 2016 Passat 1.8T SE. The *Heated driver and front passenger seats* provide warmth during colder months, while the *Leatherette seat upholstery* combines style with durability.

The vehicle s *Touchscreen* interface simplifies control over various features, making your driving experience more intuitive. Additionally, the *Selective Internet access* feature allows you to customize your digital experience, keeping you informed on local news and weather.

In summary, the 2016 Volkswagen Passat 1.8T SE is an ideal choice for anyone seeking a dependable and sophisticated sedan. With its robust safety features, luxurious comfort, and advanced technology, it stands out as an excellent option for both daily commutes and weekend adventures. Don t miss out on this fantastic vehicle act now while the price is right!

description:
2017 Honda CR-V Touring

Stock #: G26449A
Mileage: 131,671 miles
Exterior Color: White Diamond Pearl
Interior Color: Black
Drivetrain: Front-Wheel Drive (FWD)
Engine: 1.5L I4 DOHC 16V Turbocharged
Body Style: 4D Sport Utility

Overview

This 2017 Honda CR-V Touring delivers premium comfort, cutting-edge tech, and proven reliability in a stylish and practical SUV package. With a sophisticated White Diamond Pearl exterior and refined Black leather interior, this top-trim Touring edition is equipped with the features families and commuters alike appreciate all while offering Hondas trademark dependability and fuel efficiency.

With 131,671 miles, this CR-V has been driven and enjoyed but continues to be a strong performer in the compact SUV segment.

Performance & Efficiency

1.5L Turbocharged I4 Engine: Combines smooth power delivery with outstanding fuel economy.

Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT): Enhances drivability and fuel efficiency.

Front-Wheel Drive (FWD): Prioritizes efficiency and nimble handling for daily driving.

EPA-estimated fuel economy: ~28 MPG city / 34 MPG highway.

Comfort & Interior Features

The Touring trim delivers a high-end feel with a suite of premium features:

Leather-trimmed seating with power-adjustable front seats

Heated front seats for cold weather comfort

Power panoramic moonroof for open-air driving

Dual-zone automatic climate control

Memory drivers seat and mirrors

Hands-free power tailgate

Ample cargo space and smart cabin design make it ideal for family trips, grocery runs, or daily commuting.

Technology & Safety

Navigation system with voice recognition

Honda Sensing Safety Suite, including:

Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC)

Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS)

Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)

Road Departure Mitigation (RDM)

Blind Spot Information System (BSI) with Cross Traffic Monitor

7-inch touchscreen infotainment with:

Apple CarPlay and Android Auto

Bluetooth HandsFreeLink and Streaming Audio

9-speaker premium audio system with subwoofer

Summary

This 2017 Honda CR-V Touring offers top-tier safety, comfort, and technology in a well-rounded SUV. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or hauling gear, this CR-V is built to make life easier and driving more enjoyable.

Discover the perfect balance of style, capability, and technology in the 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT. This sleek and versatile crossover SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
Sun & Infotainment Package
Black Bowtie Emblems, Front and Rear (LPO)
Confidence & Convenience Package
Driver Confidence Package
Driver Convenience Package
Infotainment Package
Preferred Equipment Group 2LT
Trailering Equipment

Step inside and be captivated by the Equinox LT's refined interior. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, the connectivity of Chevrolet MyLink with an 8-inch touchscreen, and the comfort of heated front seats. The available power sunroof and rear power liftgate add a touch of luxury to your daily commute.

Under the hood, the turbocharged 2.0L engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver an impressive blend of power and efficiency, with EPA-estimated fuel economy ratings of 22 city/28 highway MPG. The available all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in any weather condition.

Safety and technology work hand-in-hand in the Equinox LT. Features like Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and Rear Park Assist provide added peace of mind on the road. Stay connected with the built-in 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot and seamlessly integrate your smartphone using Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2018 Chevrolet Equinox LT is the perfect companion. Its spacious interior, advanced technology, and impressive capabilities make it a standout in the crowded crossover segment.

Our experienced sales staff is eager to share its knowledge and enthusiasm with you. We encourage you to browse our online , schedule a test drive, and investigate financing options. All listed prices exclude taxes, license and plate fees, and a $280.00 documentation fee.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2017 MINI Cooper Clubman, a vehicle that seamlessly blends style, performance, and versatility. With its distinctive design, advanced technology, and impressive efficiency, this Clubman is poised to captivate the discerning driver.

Boasting a striking White exterior, this Clubman commands attention on the road. Complementing the sleek look are the Wheels: 17 x 7.5 Net Spoke Black Alloy, Roof Rails, and Parking Assistant, which enhance both the aesthetic and practical aspects of this vehicle. The Headliner in Anthracite adds a touch of elegance, while the 6-Speed Automatic (Steptronic) transmission provides a smooth and responsive driving experience.

Parking Assistant
Headliner In Anthracite
Wheels: 17 x 7.5 Net Spoke Black Alloy

Under the hood, the 1.5L I-3 engine, paired with the 7-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency. With a city MPG of 25 and a highway MPG of 34, this Clubman ensures you can enjoy the ride without compromising on fuel economy.

Step inside the well-appointed cabin and discover the array of features that elevate your driving experience. The MINI Connected infotainment system, with its 6.5 Visual Boost Screen, seamlessly integrates your digital world, while the SensaTec Leatherette Upholstery and Sport Steering Wheel provide a premium touch. The Split Folding Rear Seat and Roof Rails offer versatility, allowing you to adapt to your ever-changing needs.

Safety is paramount, and this Clubman is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. These cutting-edge systems work in harmony to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection.

As you embark on your next adventure, the 2017 MINI Cooper Clubman will be your steadfast companion, offering a unique blend of style, performance, and practicality. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by the exceptional qualities of this remarkable vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and safety in this 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT. With its sleek white exterior and well-appointed interior, this midsize sedan is designed to elevate your driving experience.

Standout features include:
Driver Confidence Package: Enhancing your safety with advanced driver-assist technologies like low-speed forward automatic braking, front pedestrian braking, and lane keep assist.
Convenience and Technology Package: Offering premium amenities like remote vehicle start, wireless charging, and an 8-inch Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.
1.5L DOHC engine with 6-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 27 city/36 highway MPG.

This Malibu LT is more than just a practical commuter it's a sophisticated, feature-rich sedan that elevates your daily drives. The spacious and well-appointed cabin provides ample room for passengers and cargo, while the responsive handling and available driver-assist technologies ensure a confident, controlled ride.

Safety is a top priority, and this Malibu LT is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Enjoy the peace of mind of front and rear park assist, rear cross-traffic alert, and a rearview camera, all working together to help you navigate with confidence.

Connectivity is key in today's world, and the Malibu LT delivers with the Chevrolet MyLink system. Seamlessly integrate your smartphone, stream music, and access turn-by-turn navigation all through the intuitive 8-inch touchscreen display.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, technology, and safety make it a standout choice in the midsize sedan segment.

We invite you to experience the Malibu LT for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

description: The 2019 Kia Sorento 2.4L LX, featuring the * LX Convenience Package*, is a premium SUV that blends comfort, technology, and safety seamlessly. Recently, the price has dropped by $400, presenting a perfect opportunity to act quickly before this fantastic deal disappears. Don t miss your chance to own a vehicle that promises to elevate your driving experience. Under the hood, youll find a robust 2.4L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivering an impressive 185 horsepower and paired with an efficient 6-speed automatic transmission. This combination ensures smooth performance, making it an ideal choice for both city commuting and long-distance travel. With its DOHC design and D-CVVT variable valve control, you can expect improved fuel efficiency and a satisfying driving experience. The * LX Convenience Package* enhances the Sorentos appeal, offering features such as heated driver and front passenger seats, automatic climate control, and a power-reclining driver seat. These amenities create a luxurious atmosphere that keeps you and your passengers comfortable, no matter the journey length. Safety is a top priority in the 2019 Kia Sorento. The vehicle is equipped with a rear camera and rear collision warning system, providing enhanced visibility and awareness of your surroundings. These features work together to help prevent accidents, giving you peace of mind while on the road. The brake assist feature also adds an extra layer of safety by boosting your stopping power in emergencies. Convenience is a key aspect of the Sorento, highlighted by its smart device mirroring technology. This feature allows you to easily connect your smartphone to the vehicles infotainment system, providing access to your favorite apps while keeping your focus on the road ahead. The touchscreen control adds to the convenience, enabling you to operate various functions with just a tap. Driver-centric features such as cruise control with steering wheel-mounted controls further enhance the driving experience. You can maintain your desired speed effortlessly, reducing fatigue on long trips. With multiple power adjustments for the drivers seat, including fore/aft positioning and lumbar support, finding the ideal driving position is simple and promotes safety. In summary, the 2019 Kia Sorento 2.4L LX with the * LX Convenience Package* stands out as a versatile and practical SUV that doesn t compromise on luxury. With its powerful engine, advanced technology, and comprehensive safety features, this vehicle is an ideal choice for anyone seeking a reliable and comfortable ride. description:
The 2018 Hyundai Sonata SE with the remarkable Option Group 01 is a perfect blend of style, technology, and performance, tailored for a smooth driving experience. Powered by a robust 2.4L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, it generates a commendable 185 horsepower and is paired with a seamless 6-speed automatic transmission, ensuring an efficient and dynamic ride.

One of the standout features of the Sonata SE is its Smart Device Mirroring. This cutting-edge technology allows drivers to seamlessly integrate their smartphones with the vehicles infotainment system, enhancing safety and convenience by enabling access to essential apps while keeping your focus on the road. With Smart Device Mirroring, you can enjoy your favorite playlists and navigation apps without distraction.

Safety is a top priority in the Sonata SE, exemplified by its Brake Assist feature. This innovative system senses when panic braking occurs and provides extra braking power, significantly reducing the risk of accidents during critical moments. Additionally, the Blind Spot Warning system is a game-changer, alerting drivers to vehicles in adjacent lanes, while the Rear Collision Warning feature helps mitigate accidents when reversing, ensuring peace of mind for all passengers.

Long drives become a breeze with Cruise Control and Steering Wheel Mounted Controls. These features allow you to maintain a preset speed effortlessly, helping to reduce fatigue and improve fuel efficiency on those extended trips. The Hill Hold Control technology is particularly advantageous for those navigating steep inclines, preventing the vehicle from rolling backward when starting from a stop.

Convenience is key in the Sonata SE, as demonstrated by the Keyfob Keyless Entry system. This feature enables easy access for all passengers, eliminating the need for the driver to fumble with keys when getting in or out of the vehicle. The Rear Camera further enhances safety by providing a clear view of obstacles behind you, making reversing safer and more manageable.

Connectivity is also a highlight of the Sonata SE. With Wireless Connectivity, you can make hands-free calls and access your favorite media without compromising safety. The External Memory Control feature allows you to access a variety of media stored on hard drives or memory sticks, ensuring your entertainment options are always within reach.

In summary, the 2018 Hyundai Sonata SE with the Option Group 01 offers a superb combination of performance, safety, and advanced technology, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a modern sedan. Whether youre commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, the Sonata SE is designed to make every journey enjoyable and safe.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility in this 2019 Ford Escape SEL. With its sleek silver exterior and powerful 1.5L EcoBoost engine, this SUV is ready to take on your daily adventures with confidence and efficiency.

Accident Free CARFAX History Report

Boasting an impressive 22 city/28 highway MPG rating, this Escape SEL strikes the perfect balance between power and fuel economy. Its 4WD capability ensures you'll have the traction and control you need, whether navigating winding roads or tackling inclement weather.

Inside, the spacious and well-appointed cabin provides a comfortable and connected driving experience. The SYNC 3 infotainment system seamlessly integrates with your smartphone, allowing you to access your favorite music, navigation, and more with ease. Dual-zone automatic climate control keeps you and your passengers perfectly comfortable, while the power driver's seat and heated front seats add an extra touch of luxury.

With its ample cargo space and versatile 60/40 split-folding rear seats, this Escape SEL is ready to adapt to your ever-changing lifestyle. Whether you're hauling gear for your next outdoor adventure or transporting the whole family, this SUV has the flexibility to handle it all.

Backed by Ford's renowned reputation for quality and reliability, this 2019 Escape SEL is a smart choice for the discerning driver. Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and utility schedule a test drive today and discover why this Escape could be the perfect fit for you.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of power, style, and versatility in this 2019 Dodge Durango SXT. This impressive SUV offers a commanding presence on the road, with its sleek exterior design and capable all-wheel-drive performance.

Highlights of this Durango include:
3rd Row Seating Group
SiriusXM Satellite Radio
Uconnect 4 with 7 Display
Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
Rearview Camera
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

The 3.6L V6 engine and 8-speed automatic transmission provide a smooth and responsive driving experience, delivering an impressive 25 MPG on the highway. With seating for up to 7 passengers and ample cargo space, this Durango is the perfect companion for your family adventures.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring premium cloth seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an array of advanced technology features. The Uconnect infotainment system keeps you connected and entertained, while the rearview camera and parking sensors provide added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces.

Safety is a top priority in the Durango, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Path Detection, and Full-Speed Forward Collision Warning with Active Braking.

Whether you're hauling the whole family or tackling your next weekend getaway, this 2019 Dodge Durango SXT is the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and style. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional SUV.

*Audi Long Beach does not reserve, or hold advertised vehicles, all are subject to prior sale on a first come first serve basis. Customer must take delivery of the vehicle and execute all California required documentation at Audi Long Beach. We reserve the right to revise price, equipment, mileage, and certification status as a result of changing market conditions, manufacturer/distributor notices including recall notices, or errors. All vehicle pricing expires upon close of business the same day. The stock images shown are for illustration purposes only and are not an exact representation of the actual vehicle.
Audi Long Beach presents this 2019 Volkswagen Tiguan S. This Volkswagen has 53,556 miles. Live out of the area? Contact us to discuss convenient delivery options 562-724-1463
CONDITION:
We offer a carefully curated selection of high-quality vehicles, competitively priced to deliver exceptional value. This vehicle has been meticulously inspected and reconditioned by factory trained technicians. Investing in state-of-the-art facilities, tools and training, our technicians go above and beyond the expectations of your pre-owned vehicle purchase.

BENEFITS:
There are many benefits to becoming a Fletcher Jones Owner. Complimentary services include Audi courtesy vehicles for extended repairs, complimentary pick up and delivery, multi point vehicle inspections and much more.

ABOUT US:
Audi Long Beach is a proud member of the family owned and operated Fletcher Jones Automotive Group. We ve had the pleasure of serving guests for over 70 years. This Audi center is located at 1919 North Lakewood Blvd in beautiful Long Beach, California. We offer an excellent selection of new and pre-owned Audi inventory. We likely have the vehicle you ve been searching for, or contact us to help find an exact configuration.
